{"tid":1804641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘇丹法院裁定29名情報官員虐待示威者致死罪成判死刑","createTime":"2019-12-31T06:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T07:06:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"34d1a871acb4c6671aa32245b1d468a6c0fd6d99","tid":1804641,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T06:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1500239_1_L_20191231035116.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1500239_1_L_20191231035116.jpg&h=cd72eca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蘇丹一個法院裁定29名情報官員，酷刑對待及殺死一名示威的教師，判處各被告死刑，辯方表明上訴。<br />\n<br />\n事主今年2月上街參與反政府示威，抗議執政超過30年的時任總統巴希爾管治不力，事主其後被捕。法庭接納控方指出，事主在拘留所被當局人員毆打及虐待，導致死亡。<br />\n<br />\n控方形容法庭判處死刑是伸張正義。法官在庭上問事主家人，會否希望29名被告獲得赦免，事主家人說希望立即執行刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n本案在蘇丹受到廣泛關注，大批民眾湧到位於首都喀土穆附近的城市恩圖曼，負責審理案件的法院外，等候判決結果。報道說當日事主死亡的消息傳出後，反政府浪潮及民怨更加洶湧，間接導致巴希爾在4月被發動軍事政變的軍方推翻。"},{"pid":"0f441c77073663949e69b5ac851dfdb1efaa6e24","tid":1804641,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T06:45:53.000Z","msg":"德美聯署整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804604</a>"},{"pid":"8f43a0def94e39456c3e5a2bba8cab4cfbdf2552","tid":1804641,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T06:49:20.000Z","msg":"香港衰過蘇丹"},{"pid":"dabc1d58272f574c4a04184304feacaa1e0d1f1a","tid":1804641,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T06:54:20.000Z","msg":"大快人心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"455d15f00bdf56ce599c9b882f9f8c1a4a8a3e61","tid":1804641,"uid":283712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T06:56:26.000Z","msg":"蘇丹都有公義過我地"},{"pid":"dbfc6d23cdf13e91e43e711d5c57671d9b6699f7","tid":1804641,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T07:06:06.000Z","msg":"香港係先進文明既城市，每個香港人都有獅子山精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}